csw.services.ccs

Class HcdStatusMatcherActor

  • java.lang.Object
    • csw.services.ccs.HcdStatusMatcherActor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    akka.actor.Actor, akka.actor.ActorLogging

    public class HcdStatusMatcherActor
extends java.lang.Object
implements akka.actor.Actor, akka.actor.ActorLogging
    Subscribes to the current state values of a set of HCDs and notifies the replyTo actor with the command status when they all match the respective demand states, or with an error status message if the given timeout expires.

    See props for a description of the arguments.

        replyTo - the actor to reply to
        runId - the runId to use in the reply
        timeout - the amount of time to wait for a match before giving up and replying with a Timeout message
